OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC has apologised to Nigel Farage 
OL,6, over its inaccurate report about why   
OL,7, his account at Coutts bank was closed. 
OL,9,FOn 4 July, the BBC reported Mr Farage  
OL,10,Fno longer met the financial            
OL,11,Frequirements for Coutts, citing a      
OL,12,Fsource familiar with the matter.       
OL,14,FThe former UKIP leader later obtained a
OL,15,FCoutts report which indicated his      
OL,16,Fpolitical views were also considered.  
OL,18,FMr Farage said he accepted the         
OL,19,Fapologies "with good grace", but said  
OL,20,Fquestions for Coutts remained.         
